# Agentic Network RCA

A **multi-agent system** for automated **Root Cause Analysis (RCA)** of
network issues.  The system ingests time-series network metrics, detects
statistical and threshold-based anomalies, maps them to root-cause
hypotheses using rule-based reasoning, and produces structured reports
with actionable remediation steps.

---

## Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                      RCAOrchestrator                            │
│                                                                 │
│  ┌──────────────────┐   ┌───────────────────────┐              │
│  │ DataIngestion    │──▶│ AnomalyDetection       │             │
│  │ Agent            │   │ Agent                  │             │
│  │                  │   │ (sliding-window z-score│             │
│  │ • load JSON file │   │  + absolute thresholds)│             │
│  │ • or simulate    │   └───────────┬───────────┘              │
│  │   synthetic data │               │                           │
│  └──────────────────┘               ▼                           │
│                        ┌────────────────────────┐              │
│                        │ RCA Agent              │              │
│                        │ (pattern-matching rules│              │
│                        │  → root-cause hypotheses│             │
│                        │  with confidence scores)│             │
│                        └───────────┬────────────┘              │
│                                    │                            │
│                                    ▼                            │
│                        ┌────────────────────────┐              │
│                        │ Report Agent           │              │
│                        │ (assemble RCAReport    │              │
│                        │  + write JSON / text)  │              │
│                        └────────────────────────┘              │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Agents

| Agent | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| **DataIngestionAgent** | Load metrics from JSON or generate synthetic data for one of five built-in scenarios |
| **AnomalyDetectionAgent** | Flag deviations using a sliding-window z-score (≥ 2.5 σ) combined with absolute thresholds per metric type |
| **RCAAgent** | Match sets of anomalous metric types against pattern rules (congestion, hardware failure, misconfiguration, resource exhaustion, throughput degradation) and compute confidence scores |
| **ReportAgent** | Assemble a structured `RCAReport`, optionally write it as JSON or plain text |

### Simulation Scenarios

| Scenario | Injected fault |
|---|---|
| `congestion` | High bandwidth utilisation → latency + packet-loss spikes |
| `hardware_failure` | Elevated error rate + packet loss |
| `misconfiguration` | Jitter spike, fragmentation errors |
| `resource_exhaustion` | CPU / memory saturation |
| `normal` | Healthy baseline — no anomalies |

